con:testSuite.name: TestSuite
con:testSuite.con:description:
Tests the Readonly Product Service by...
Checking the getServiceInformation operation. Performing a findByManufacturerName. Performing a findByCategoryId for the category of the first product returned in the last test. Performing a getProduct for the first product returned in the last test.

con:testCase.name: findAndGetByCategoryName
con:testCase.con:description:
findAllCategories: Gets a list of all the known categories and selects the first one in the list to use for the remainder of the test suite.
findByCategoryName: Finds and lists all the products in the given category. Selects the Id of the first product to use for the remainder of the suite.
getProduct: Gets the product information of the Product described by the current ProductId in the test Properties.

con:transfers.con:name: CategoryName
ProductId

con:testCase.name: findAndGetByManufacturerName
con:testCase.con:description:
findAllManufacturers: Gets a list of all the known manufacturers and selects the first one in the list to use for the remainder of the test suite.
findByManufacturerName: Finds and lists all the products manufactured by the given manufacturer. Selects the Id of the first product to use for the remainter of the suite.
getProduct: Gets the product information of the Product described by the current ProductId in the test Properties.

con:transfers.con:name: ManufacturerName
ProductId

con:testCase.name: getServiceInformation
con:testCase.con:description: getServiceInformation: Tests that the service information can be retrieved.
